text.section:
An application for the establishment or relocation of a branch office or relocation of a principal office shall include:
An application fee of $500 unless the application is for relocation within a one-half mile radius of the existing site; and
A statement of:
The need for the establishment or relocation;
The address of the proposed location;
The services to be provided;
The estimated annual expense; and
The source of payment for the annual expense.
